            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Numini Saturno <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>reg</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> patri deo<lb break="no" n="3"/>rum </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et Latonae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> R<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ecius</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>Primus ben<lb break="no" n="4"/><expan><abbr>ef</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>V <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>acedonicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> ex <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>oto</ex></expan> domo Zigali </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Afer
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Basis noch die untere Hälfte einer thronenden männlichen Statue. Z. 1-3 auf der corona, Z. 9 auf der crepido. Datierung: Stationierung der legio V Macedonica in Potaissa ab 166/167 n. Chr. Z. 8: Buchstabe Z spiegelverkehrt geschrieben. (B): ILD; Bertrandy: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
